multiFactorAuthenticationWarning.comment: Message to show the end user when Multi Factor Authentication needs to be performed to access restricted information.
multiFactorAuthenticationWarning.value: Multi Factor Authentication is required for components to render correctly.

disablePopUpBlockerWarning.comment: Message to show the end user when pop up blocker is enabled on the current page.
disablePopUpBlockerWarning.value: Pop up blocker must be disabled for components on this page to render. Please disable pop up blocker and refresh the page.
